description:
An early collection of Peter Kuper's short story work. Mostly b&amp;w, with some small splashes of red. As with everything he's done, uniquely original artwork and panels abound. But as this is a collection of shorter stories done separately over a period of about two years (1988-89) it contains several different styles or artwork. 

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

It's Only a Matter of Life and Death

Peter Kuper

Fantagraphics, 1990, 44 pages
